pme.ai.fhe.de.studybuddy.model

Class Module

  • java.lang.Object
    • pme.ai.fhe.de.studybuddy.model.Module

  • public class Module
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the module entity. It has a foreign key connection to a course_id. This stands for the course to which the lecture belongs.
